{
  "texts": [
    "To what degree does increasing the specificity of prompts impact the structure and content of AI-generated lesson plans?",
    "There was a marginally significant difference in overall trends of prompt scores between prompt groups (p = 0.0442, F = 2.668, DF = 4), though significance was not supported in multiple testcorrected pairwise tests (p > 0.12).",
    "Adding detailed instructions had the effect of reducing the spread of variance and in some cases raising the mean value of scores (Figure 1).",
    "However, the mean scores did not increase linearly as a function of prompt detail.",
    "When the lesson template was first provided in P.3, the mean score dropped from 21.2 out of 25 from P.2 to 19.8."
  ]
}